Package: deepscanscape
Type: Package
Title: Annotate New Data Using Deep Mutational Landscapes
Version: 0.0.0.9006
Authors@R: person("Alistair", "Dunham", email = "ally@ebi.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Process and annotate new deep mutational scanning study data
    based on a deep mutational landscape derived from 28 previous studies.
    It allows new data to be standardised and compared to these studies to 
    detect unusual results and positions to be annotated with results from the 
    combined dataset, including the caclulated amino acid subtypes.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
